  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "67fcfe606c550fec625d1cb3",
      "text": "GPT文体",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7be",
      "text": "「[GPT][文体]」とは、ChatGPTのような言語モデルが生成するテキストに特有の文体や言語的特徴を指す、やや曖昧な言い回しですが、いくつかの共通的な傾向があります。以下にその特徴をまとめます：",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633551
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7bf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7c0",
      "text": "[/icons/hr.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7c1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7c2",
      "text": "[** 🧠 GPT文体の主な特徴]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7c3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7c4",
      "text": "[** 1. 論理的で整然とした構成]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7c5",
      "text": " 序論 → 本論 → 結論という構成が多い。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7c6",
      "text": " 論点が明確で、説明は段階的（ステップバイステップ）。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7c7",
      "text": " 話の流れを丁寧にガイドする表現が多い（例：「まず」「次に」「最後に」など）。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7c8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7c9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7ca",
      "text": "[** 2. 丁寧で中立的な言葉遣い]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7cb",
      "text": " 主観を避け、客観的に書く傾向。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7cc",
      "text": " 批判や感情的表現を避け、柔らかく婉曲的に述べる。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7cd",
      "text": " 敬語や丁寧語が多用される（日本語の場合）。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7ce",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7d0",
      "text": "[** 3. 過剰な明確化（Overclarification）]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7d1",
      "text": " 相手が知っているかもしれないことも、前提から丁寧に説明する。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7d2",
      "text": " 「簡単に言えば」「つまり」「言い換えると」など、説明補助の言葉が多い。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7d3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7d4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7d5",
      "text": "[** 4. 例示と要約が多い]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7d6",
      "text": " よく使われる表現：「例えば」「このように」「要するに」など。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7d7",
      "text": " 複雑な概念を噛み砕いて説明する工夫がある。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7d8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7da",
      "text": "[** 5. バランスの取れた表現]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7db",
      "text": " 断定を避け、「〜かもしれません」「〜という可能性があります」など、控えめな語尾を使う。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7dc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7de",
      "text": "[/icons/hr.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7df",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7e0",
      "text": "[** 🧪 例文：GPT文体のサンプル]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7e1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7e2",
      "text": "[* 通常の文：]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7e3",
      "text": "> AIは人間の仕事を奪う可能性がある。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7e5",
      "text": "[* GPT文体：]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7e6",
      "text": "> AIの進化に伴い、一部の仕事が自動化される可能性があります。ただし、すべての職種が影響を受けるわけではなく、新たな職種が生まれる可能性も指摘されています。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7e8",
      "text": "[/icons/hr.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7e9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7ea",
      "text": "[** 🎯 GPT文体がよく使われる場面]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7eb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7ec",
      "text": " 説明文、解説記事、FAQ",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7ed",
      "text": " 学術的または技術的な内容の要約",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7ee",
      "text": " 丁寧なビジネス文章やメールの下書き",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7ef",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7f0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7f1",
      "text": "[/icons/hr.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7f2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7f3",
      "text": "もし何かの文章が「GPTっぽい」と言われたら、それは「論理的すぎて人間味が薄い」や「やけに丁寧すぎる」といったニュアンスを含むこともあります。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fcfeac0000000000a1b7f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744633516,
      "updated": 1744633516
    },
    {
      "id": "67fd01dc0000000000a1b7f9",
      "text": "GPT-3.5時代はもっと簡潔だった気がする",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1744634333,
      "updated": 1744634341
    },
    {
      "id": "67fd01df0000000000a1b7fa",
